{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ANGELS X DEMONS SOULSLIKE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/os.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Depths of Despair aims to capture the engaging progression of MMOs with a souls-like combat experience in a brutal and atmospheric dark fantasy setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leveling system for easy and non-punishing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring atleast 6 skill trees with over 296 different abilities and perks combined, offering a huge amount of customization options and fun progression paths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/SkillTreeGif.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features four distinct combat styles: melee, magic, archery, and summoning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/combatnew.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable follower Amelia, with her own skill tree and attribute points, can be summoned and dismissed at will.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skills, stats, and everything can be changed on the fly without restrictions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allowing the player to freely experiment with different combinations and try out new approaches as they prefer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Depths of Despair</strong> tells a story of demons finally finding a way to invade Heaven. The reason for the invasion is, of course, domination, but the main motive is the blood of angels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Angel blood grants god-like powers to demons and acts like a highly addictive drug. This sparks a new age of fear and horror in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One of the angels, Amelia, desperately goes after the captured angels in an effort to save them, one of whom is her sister. After a long and grueling ordeal in the Dungeon of Lost Souls, she finds a chosen soldier to aid her on the perilous journey.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2976770?t=1739960289","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2976770?t=1739960289","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/308ec6291e49ca8e2892cffbaefa063d3a11432a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739960289","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/308ec6291e49ca8e2892cffbaefa063d3a11432a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739960289","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ANGELS X DEMONS SOULSLIKE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/os.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Depths of Despair aims to capture the engaging progression of MMOs with a souls-like combat experience in a brutal and atmospheric dark fantasy setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leveling system for easy and non-punishing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring atleast 6 skill trees with over 296 different abilities and perks combined, offering a huge amount of customization options and fun progression paths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/SkillTreeGif.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features four distinct combat styles: melee, magic, archery, and summoning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/extras/combatnew.gif?t=1739960289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable follower Amelia, with her own skill tree and attribute points, can be summoned and dismissed at will.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skills, stats, and everything can be changed on the fly without restrictions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allowing the player to freely experiment with different combinations and try out new approaches as they prefer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Depths of Despair</strong> tells a story of demons finally finding a way to invade Heaven. The reason for the invasion is, of course, domination, but the main motive is the blood of angels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Angel blood grants god-like powers to demons and acts like a highly addictive drug. This sparks a new age of fear and horror in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One of the angels, Amelia, desperately goes after the captured angels in an effort to save them, one of whom is her sister. After a long and grueling ordeal in the Dungeon of Lost Souls, she finds a chosen soldier to aid her on the perilous journey.</p>","developers":["herbeni"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976770/header.jpg?t=1739960289","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257097535,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097535/movie480.mp4?t=1739398164","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097535/movie_max.mp4?t=1739398164"},"name":"Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257097535/d5cf404f820b256f5af97f26773393c320f80d2c/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739398164","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097535/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739398164","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097535/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739398164"}}],"name":"The Depths of Despair","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> INTEL CORE I5-8400 or AMD RYZEN 3 3300X<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 12 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GEFORCE GTX 1060 3 GB or AMD RADEON RX 580 4 GB<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 12<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 60 GB available s